is research is qualitative research with the type of field research. The data collection techniques in this research are: (1) Observation, which aims to observe conditions in the field related to the implementation of CSR in improving the community's economy, (2) Interview, which aims to obtain in-depth information from several related informants, (3) Documentation Study, which the aim is to obtain data through existing documents in the form of archives related to CSR implementation related to company profile, history, vision and mission, organizational structure, CSR implementation reports related to research problems. Analysis of the data used through analysis activities before and after in the field. Data analysis before going to the field was carried out by studying literature reviews and secondary data. Data analysis in the field is carried out by data reduction, descriptive data presentation, verification and drawing conclusions.}{\rtlch \fcs1 \af6 \afs22 \ltrch \fcs0 \i1 \fs22 \rtlch \alang1025 \ltrch \dbch \af0 \hich \af6 \loch \f6 \lang1033 \langnp1033 \langfe1033 \langfenp1033 \alang1025 \par }\pard \plain \s34 \qj \li0 \ri0 \lisb0 \sa160 \lisa0 \sl240 \slmult1 \widctlpar \aspalpha \aspnum \adjustright \lin0 \rin0 \itap0 \rtlch \fcs1 \af6 \afs22 \ltrch \fcs0 \fs22 \rtlch \alang1025 \ltrch \loch \af7 \hich \af7 \dbch \af0 \lang1057 \langnp1057 \langfe1033 \langfenp1033 \alang1025 {\rtlch \fcs1 \af6 \afs22 \ltrch \fcs0 \i1 \fs22 \rtlch \alang1025 \ltrch \dbch \af0 \hich \af6 \loch \f6 \lang1033 \langnp1033 \langfe1033 \langfenp1033 \alang1025 The research results show that the implementation of PT PLN Indonesia Power UP Indralaya's CSR has taken place from planning activities to the monitoring and evaluation stages of the CSR program. The research results also show that the implementation of CSR has had a positive impact on society which has led to economic improvements such as increasing people's income, providing employment opportunities, environmental management activities, and increasing people's knowledge and skills.}{\rtlch \fcs1 \af6 \afs22 \ltrch \fcs0 \i1 \fs22 \rtlch \alang1025 \ltrch \dbch \af0 \hich \af6 \loch \f6 \lang1033 \langnp1033 \langfe1033 \langfenp1033 \alang1025 \par }\pard \plain \s34 \li0 \ri0 \lisb0 \sa160 \lisa0 \sl240 \slmult1 \widctlpar \aspalpha \aspnum \adjustright \lin0 \rin0 \itap0 \rtlch \fcs1 \af6 \afs22 \ltrch \fcs0 \fs22 \rtlch \alang1025 \ltrch \loch \af7 \hich \af7 \dbch \af0 \lang1057 \langnp1057 \langfe1033 \langfenp1033 \alang1025 {\rtlch \fcs1 \af0 \afs24 \ltrch \fcs0 \fs24 \rtlch \alang1025 \ltrch \dbch \af0 \hich \af7 \loch \f0 \lang1033 \langnp1033 \langfe1033 \langfenp1033 \alang1025 \par }\pard \plain \qj \li0 \ri0 \lisb0 \sa160 \lisa0 \sl240 \slmult1 \widctlpar \aspalpha \aspnum \adjustright \lin0 \rin0 \itap0 \rtlch \fcs1 \af6 \afs22 \ltrch \fcs0 \fs22 \rtlch \alang1025 \ltrch \loch \af7 \hich \af7 \dbch \af0 \lang1057 \langnp1057 \langfe1033 \langfenp1033 \alang1025 {\rtlch \fcs1 \af6 \afs22 \ltrch \fcs0 \b1 \i1 \fs22 \rtlch \alang1025 \ltrch \dbch \af0 \hich \af6 \loch \f6 \lang1033 \langnp1033 \langfe1033 \langfenp1033 \alang1025 Keywords: Analysis, Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR), Improving the Community Economy in Payakabung Village.}{\rtlch \fcs1 \af6 \afs22 \ltrch \fcs0 \b1 \i1 \fs22 \rtlch \alang1025 \ltrch \dbch \af0 \hich \af6 \loch \f6 \lang1033 \langnp1033 \langfe1033 \langfenp1033 \alang1025 \par }\pard \plain \s34 \qc \li0 \ri0 \lisb0 \sa200 \lisa0 \sl240 \slmult1 \widctlpar \aspalpha \aspnum \adjustright \lin0 \rin0 \itap0 \rtlch \fcs1 \af6 \afs22 \ltrch \fcs0 \fs22 \rtlch \alang1025 \ltrch \loch \af7 \hich \af7 \dbch \af0 \lang1057 \langnp1057 \langfe1033 \langfenp1033 \alang1025 {\rtlch \fcs1 \af0 \afs24 \ltrch \fcs0 \fs24 \rtlch \alang1025 \ltrch \dbch \af0 \hich \af7 \loch \f0 \lang1033 \langnp1033 \langfe1033 \langfenp1033 \alang1025 \par }\pard \plain \s34 \qc \li0 \ri0 \lisb0 \sa200 \lisa0 \sl240 \slmult1 \widctlpar \aspalpha \aspnum \adjustri